                    <h3>Lecturing</h3>

<p>My main interests are:</p>

<ul>
<li>software development</li>
<li>user experience design</li>
<li>front-end development</li>
<li>web design and development</li>
<li>css,js,php,cms (WP, Grav, Processwire)</li>
<li>fullstack JS frameworks (Angular, MEAN)</li>
<li>arduino, gadgeteer micro-controllers</li>
</ul>
</div>
            </div>
            <div class="span5">
                <img class="pull-right" width=200px height=200px src="content/about/me.png"></img>
                <div>
                    <h3>Other work</h3>

<p>I am currently programme chair for Software. I administer third and fourth year projects across three programmes - software, games &amp; web dev. If you have an idea for a project or have an interest in having some students take a look at a problem, contact me.</p>

<p>I also entertain collaboration with industry in differing aspects of software/hardware development. Or if you have an interest in undertaking post-graduate work or industrial partnership, feel free to make contact.</p>

<h4>Student Queries</h4>

<p>Students are welcome to meet me for queries and arranged project meetings at the following specified times:</p>

<ul>
<li>Monday 10-1</li>
<li>Wednesday 9-1</li>
<li>Thursday 9-11</li>
</ul>

<p>Do note however that most queries have their answer on this site so please consult it in the first instance.</p>
                </div>
